{"tid":1304020,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［認真］大家要打低TVB就要繼續支持保礦力","createTime":"2019-07-10T13:20:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-11T06:01:21.000Z","uid":1251,"like":78,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"c539919cedd6256f3692401374f049225139fee5","tid":1304020,"uid":1251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T13:20:58.000Z","msg":"雖然出左張公告<br />\n但入面冇乜實質內容<br />\n好明顯係交差用<br />\n<br />\n大家要明白<br />\n作為商家點都要做下門面野<br />\n<br />\n一日唔係TVB賣返廣告都唔算跪低<br />\n門面野又由佢做黎交差囉<br />\n<br />\n總之佢唔幫襯TVB就目的已達<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">如果而家大家調轉槍頭<br />\n會嚇怕其他考慮緊仲係唔係TVB落廣告既公司<br />\n</span></span><br />\n所以我地要繼續支持保礦力<br />\n做一個成功既例子俾其他公司睇<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">只要佢地肯唔再係TVB賣廣告<br />\n我地就會不斷支持佢</span></span><br />\n<br />\n業績係最好既證明！"},{"pid":"8f1391df476b94af5a4c938c6956087622aeae2c","tid":1304020,"uid":1251,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T13:21:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23478c95c83ad884a9ebc6449de960f580ae31cc","tid":1304020,"uid":1251,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T13:23:46.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">冇炒車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"01e46bac2990ed26bbb3843ab89f6ed326955499","tid":1304020,"uid":36321,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T13:23:50.000Z","msg":"即係同當日pp一樣<br />\n俾人入場玩行為藝術點都咋下型<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58a0c505a14c6f2ed489b32ac38113d4d71d65e2","ti